{"tid":403684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯條仆街話撐港獨要「殺無赦」，係咪可以告刑事恐嚇？","createTime":"2017-09-17T11:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T12:18:15.000Z","uid":134251,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5216442127935edcbecd5e6c4b93186de3170d64","tid":403684,"uid":134251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:44:03.000Z","msg":"【反冷血&hellip;&hellip;】<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/?p=229504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F%3Fp%3D229504&d=GZt96%2FKv4wIU%2FOEQMyNF7QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=12cdc43a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/?p=229504</a><br />\n<br />\n「反港獨、反冷血、反偽學&mdash;革走戴耀廷呐喊大會」於今午5時許結束，大會稱有4,000千參與，發起人立法會議員何君堯見傳媒時一度質疑記者的問題「膚淺」，表示是次集會群情淘湧，亦並非無的放矢或毫無根據，呼籲大家不要輕看「小雨點」的力量、「用數字嚟挑機」。被問到屏山鄉鄉事委員會主席曾樹和在台上表明「搞港獨要殺」，會否構成刑事恐嚇，何君堯則稱「殺豬殺狗唔係咩刑事嘅」，坦言記者有關提問為無謂、多餘，不應斷章取義；當記者追問何謂「殺無赦」時，他回應稱是意指「嫉惡如仇」，而「港獨」提倡者企圖顛覆國家命運，令13億人口須為其付出龐大代價，「呢啲人唔殺咗佢做咩」。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯續指，日後亦會展開「革走陳健民」的行動，或會稍後去信中大要求辭退陳健民社會學系副教授一職，惟要「一步一步做」。至於港大，他表示假若校方回覆時明言，並無表證證實他信中關於戴耀廷的指控，並不接受投訴，便會提出司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n#852郵報 #戴耀廷 #港獨 #何君堯 #殺無赦 #陳健民"},{"pid":"f167cc24d4c21b558f2377e0c53be2b435c0a95c","tid":403684,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"用仆街形容佢好似唔夠貼切，佢同啫融邊個衰啲"},{"pid":"10bd1e3eef4766952e7d386d26ca8921298e66f9","tid":403684,"uid":138613,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n何君堯呢啲契弟<br />\n永遠都只會趨炎附勢<br />\n諗住做多啲就可以上位<br />\n人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連要殺人都可以講得出<br />\n不過睇死啲差佬都係唔會檢控佢"},{"pid":"75d809dc3ce3bff26e7b503bebabf8ed8ae3ce7f","tid":403684,"uid":35094,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"殺豬殺狗唔係咩刑事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f450304c966d58b2093b0292ef97d3fe05c92b9e","tid":403684,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"港版既文化大革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93f40241484098f8faf16311bfc3526958fa861","tid":403684,"uid":132302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T12:14:30.000Z","msg":"哎sor 律政司表示見唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f563af1acde1f95c22beaf1285ee601070ec8097","tid":403684,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T12:15:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc63094bd6e1df1f0defe4014d42e978bac3286","tid":403684,"uid":13115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T12:16:05.000Z","msg":"出街小心呀何老妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3da6d4263ef5f8feb2f00243a530058ece4f4a","tid":403684,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T12:16:26.000Z","msg":"知法犯法。。。<br />\n可以取消佢律師資格。。。"},{"pid":"465db89914462d453b88f6ed6b1049c9ad5481d1","tid":403684,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T12:16:32.000Z","msg":"條仆街愈黎愈癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd83d548a5e858c6efe8c1957868d532613f591f","tid":403684,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T12:17:13.000Z","msg":"可唔可以向律師會投訴?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n澳洲籍民賤聯粗口大狀馬恩國都比大律師公會罰釘一個月牌啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3f2ce40c45c66a941c4811529f472cbb6142a